                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1341" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0215</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8509 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财富加，家天下：“鑫梅花”的全新绽放</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wealth increasing and family sharing：The blossom of Xinmeihua</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何健</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鑫梅花；财富加；品牌管理；家天下</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xinmeihua; Brand Management; Family Sharing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自诞生以来，城市商业银行一直处于激烈的同业竞争中，大型中资银行、外资银行在中国金融业中长期占据主导地位。为了向高端个人客户提供更具个性化、更高附加值、更周到全面的财富管理，南京银行推出了“鑫梅花”金融服务品牌。本文描述了“鑫梅花”金融服务品牌从品牌规划、品牌定位、品牌战略制定到品牌沟通这一品牌管理过程。“鑫梅花”金融服务品牌是南京银行提升公司品牌与理财品牌的重要战略部署。在总行的大力支持下，通过对行业背景、竞争者与目标市场的分析，秉承“财富加，家天下”的理念，“鑫梅花”金融服务品牌直接定位于兼顾财富增长和家庭尊崇感受的高端客户，在品牌名称、服务环境等方面做了精心设计，遵循“尊贵、周到、私密”的原则制定了品牌战略，注重大众传播与精准圈层传播相结合，深化品牌推广，不断提升品牌知名度。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The case describes how smaller banks in China respond when they face challenges from both foreign banks and large state-controlled banks in the area of private wealth management. In the process of the development of financial services, foreign banks and large state-controlled banks have been the leaders all the time, while smaller banks can do almost nothing to adapt to the innovation in financial products and fall into the homogeneous competition instead. So, what can they do to get a piece of the pie? The brand Xinmeihua of Nanjing Bank holds lessons for the peers because it walks its own way. Different from other banks, the positioning of Xinmeihua is the happiness of a family instead of the dignity of an individual. However, the market reaction remains to be a problem and it is not assured that its potential clients will accept it. In addition, will the senior managers keep the support of this brand and will the Xinmeihua brand have a bright future? This combination of challenges and opportunities is producing a fizzing cocktail of creativity. Ms Liu, as the director of the Xinmeihua department, feels ambitious and has long to go. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌管理的战术流程、品牌更新的运用条件和效果评估</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-10</td>
                            </tr>
